.:: Zebra puzzle ::.
There are 5 different favourite colors: purple, white, amber, lavender, blood-red
There are 5 different nationalities: mexican, indonesian, nigerian, dutch, italian
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: blend, swisher, game, siglo, bolivar
There are 5 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, soy-sprite, sprite, lemonade, juice
5 different pets are kept: rat, hedgehog, goldfish, snake, fish

1. the mexican is the person who likes purple
2. the indonesian is the owner of the rat
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person who likes white
4. the nigerian is the person drinking soy-sprite
5. the person who likes white is to the right of the person who likes amber
6. the blend-smoker is the owner of the fish
7. the swisher-smoker is the person who likes lavender
8. the person drinking sprite is in the middle
9. the dutch is on the far left
10. the game-smoker is on the left or right of the owner of the hedgehog
11. the swisher-smoker is to the left or right of the owner of the snake
12. the siglo-smoker is the person drinking lemonade
13. the italian is the bolivar-smoker
14. the dutch is to the left or right of the person who likes blood-red

.:: Answer ::.
|		|       1	|	2	|	3 	|	4	|	5	|
| Nationality	|   dutch	|    nigerian	|     mexican	|    indonesian	|    italian	|
| Color		|    lavender	|      blood-red	|      purple	|     amber	|     white	|
| Beverage	|     juice	|      soy-sprite	|      sprite	| lemonade	|     hot-chocolate	|
| Cigar		|     swisher	| chesterfield	|    olg-gold	| siglo	|   parliament	|
| Pet		|     hedgehog	|     snake	|     fish	|     rat	|     goldfish	|
